                            <comment id="14097282" author="cheolsoo" created="Thu, 14 Aug 2014 18:53:40 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching a patch that introduces a new property &lt;tt&gt;pig.streaming.udf.python.command&lt;/tt&gt;. I also documented streaming-related properties in &lt;tt&gt;pig.properties&lt;/tt&gt; file.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14097286" author="daijy" created="Thu, 14 Aug 2014 18:55:48 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14097350" author="cheolsoo" created="Thu, 14 Aug 2014 19:33:14 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed to trunk. Thanks Daniel for the review!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14097649" author="cheolsoo" created="Thu, 14 Aug 2014 21:59:59 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;One minor fix. I also need to change the following one line in StreamingUDF.java-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
     &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;boolean&lt;/span&gt; isPython() {
-        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; language.toLowerCase().equals(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;python&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
+        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; language.toLowerCase().startsWith(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;python&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
     }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14172502" author="msukmanowsky" created="Wed, 15 Oct 2014 16:57:00 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Awesome, thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=cheolsoo&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;cheolsoo&quot;&gt;Cheolsoo Park&lt;/a&gt;! So we&apos;ll be able to use this with &lt;tt&gt;SET pig.streaming.udf.python.command &apos;/path/to/virtualenv/bin/python&apos;&lt;/tt&gt;? Wasn&apos;t sure if that would invalidate your &lt;tt&gt;language.toLowerCase()&lt;/tt&gt; clause above. Perhaps needs to be&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;boolean&lt;/span&gt; isPython() {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; language.toLowerCase().indexOf(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;python&quot;&lt;/span&gt;) != -1;
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
